NOTE ON BUNDLED CONTENT

This repository aggregates skills from multiple upstream projects (see the
README for the source list). Each `skills/<name>/` directory may carry its
own license inherited from its upstream source. The MIT license above
applies to this repository's curation and the scripts/workflows in `/`,
`/scripts/`, and `/.github/` — not to the upstream skill content itself.
Consult the upstream repository linked in the README and any LICENSE
file inside a skill directory before reusing skill content commercially.
